descriptionHtml:
This is just an aesthetic change to Cicero\'s garb in the game. It changes his costume to a more drab charcoal shade, with blood stains. First mod, I apologize for any inconsistencies. I will make changes as I go, because there\'s always something more.

This replaces only the male jester set in the game, as this was crafted with Cicero in mind.

Just place the textures folder into;
Program files(x86)/Steam/SteamApps/Common/Skyrim/Data

Enjoy.
author: Brisa
